Create EC2 Instance:

-Name: Company-Web-Server
-AMI: Amazon Linux
-Instance Type: t2.micro

Security Groups used:
-SSH port 22
-HTTP port 80


Terminal connection:
-ssh -i mykey.pem ec2-user@PUBLIC-IP

Install Apache
-sudo yum update -y
-sudo yum install httpd -y
-sudo stemct1 start http

Create Website
-sudo nano /var/www/html/index.html

open in browser
-http://EC2-public-IP
